### A utility function to swap two elements 
### Array, A-position, B-position

Func SwapQS ( arr, a, b ) 
    t      = arr[a] 
    arr[a] = arr[b] 
    arr[b] = t 
return 
  

###============================================================= 
### This function is same in both iterative and recursive
### Array, LowBound, HighBound, Pivot is HighBound Element

Func Partition (arr, L, H) 

    x = arr[H] 
    i = L-1        
    
        for j = L to (H -1)
            if (arr[j] <= x)         
                i++ 
                SwapQS (arr, i, j)   
                swapCount++
                arrayAccess++
            ok 
        next
    
    SwapQS (arr, (i + 1), H) 
    swapCount++
    
return (i + 1)


